    "Coders were fluent in two or more languages of the output.",
    "Our intercoder reliability test produced a Krippendorff's alpha coefficient of 0.8 as an average for all five variables, which we considered satisfactory for the analysis.",
    "The remaining disagreements were consensus coded.To analyse data, we used a combination of descriptive statistics and regression analysis.",
